  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_134",
    "english": "Among the orcs of the Demon Realm, these kinds have completely settled in the human world, doing tough work for a living. Orcs who have gained experience in crime syndicates of the human world mostly claim their place as the assault commander. With a crude fireaxe and shield to depend their lives on, an orc leading their men into battle is a feared subject among civilians who live in the underworld.",
